Package: wickragym
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Gymnasium-Compatible Backtest Environment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-gym over its C ABI hub: build a
    Gymnasium-compatible backtest environment from a JSON spec, load candles and
    drive it with reset/step commands - the same JSON protocol as the CLI and
    every other language binding, with byte-identical trajectories.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-gym
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-gym/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-gym C ABI shared library (WKGYM_LIB) and its
    header (WKGYM_INC).
Suggests: jsonlite
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
